rComments: Amazing instructor. I bug him during office hours, and trust me he is really helpful! When you ask him for help in a question during O.H, he wont give you an answer. He will make YOU do it, which is what I like in a prof.
Keeps a good pace in class, a bit fast but not so fast that you ever get lost. He explains the concepts clearly and thoroughly and is doing a good job overall.

Prof Yacobi is one of the smartest profs in math, in my opinion. However He is FAST!! He speaks so fast you dont understand what he says!  And when he completes writing on the board he immediately jumps to the next topic leaving students a bit confused. He needs to slow down thats all. Otherwise he is good and very helfpul.
He is very young for a professor, very helpful and clear, enthusiastic, and knowledgeable. Highly recommend him
